The advanced vertical fog shader supports Standard, LWRP, URP

1. Create 3D Object - Plane
2. Create Material, drop Advanced Vertical Fog on top of it
3. Apply the Material to the Plane

If developing for mobile and the fog is completely transparent, attach the script from "Fix" folder to your Main Camera

